OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1776795065
OL,3,CReform UK closes gap on Plaid Cymru in
OL,4,Crace to become Senedd's largest party
OL,6,FReform UK has closed the gap on Plaid
OL,7,FCymru in the race to become the
OL,8,Flargest party in the Senedd, according
OL,9,Fto ITV Cymru Wales' latest poll.
OL,11,FThe two parties have consistently
OL,12,Fpolled neck-and-neck but Reform UK has
OL,13,Fincreased its vote share - while Plaid
OL,14,Fhas seen a drop - since our last poll,
OL,15,Fpositioning both parties now tied at
OL,16,F29%.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
