SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1776795065
OL,3,CReform UK closes gap on Plaid Cymru in
OL,4,Crace to become Senedd's largest party
OL,6,FThe Welsh Conservatives are up one
OL,7,Fpercentage point to 8% which would
OL,8,Fbring three seats, although this round
OL,9,Fof results would not return leader
OL,10,FDarren Millar.
OL,12,FThe Welsh Liberal Democrats are also
OL,13,Fup one percentage point to 6% which,
OL,14,Fin this scenario, would elect just one
OL,15,Fmember - their leader Jane Dodds.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
