PN,46208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1776795065
OL,3,CReform UK closes gap on Plaid Cymru in
OL,4,Crace to become Senedd's largest party
OL,6,FAdrian Masters, ITV Cymru Wales'
OL,7,FPolitical Editor said: "For the two
OL,8,Ffrontrunners, this poll will have a
OL,9,Fgalvanising effect. Reform UK will use
OL,10,Fit to urge its supporters to make its
OL,11,Fgain a reality in terms of votes.
OL,12,FWhile Plaid Cymru's drop won't
OL,13,Fnecessarily be unwelcome to that
OL,14,Fparty, shaking up any complacency that
OL,15,Fmay have crept in over the months when
OL,16,Fits lead was clearer.
OL,26,@oD@XOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
