FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1776795065
OL,3,CReform UK closes gap on Plaid Cymru in
OL,4,Crace to become Senedd's largest party
OL,6,F"However, the main message remains the
OL,7,Fsame: the vote on May 7th shows every
OL,8,Fsign of being a change election.
OL,9,FVoters here in Wales have clearly
OL,10,Fdecided that they want something
OL,11,Fdifferent, but they haven't yet
OL,12,Fsettled on what form that change will
OL,13,Ftake."
OL,15,FWhich parties would represent you
OL,16,Faccording to ITV Wales' seat
OL,17,Fprojection? Use our interactive map to
OL,18,Fsee a full breakdown of who is
OL,19,Fprojected to win in your constituency.
